summary:
20 years of patent law practice, qualified as patent attorney, US lawyer and UK solicitor. Based in Amsterdam, advising on matters under both European and US law.  
10 years of experience as an electrical engineer before beginning law practice.

Specialties: Focused on patent litigation, prosecution, and counseling, in the electronic, telecommunications, semiconductor, and computer technologies. Based in Amsterdam, advising on matters under both European and US law. Widely involved in multi-jurisdictional patent disputes.
